OL,4,Cname 68-year-old man who died
OL,6,FPolice have named a man who died
OL,7,Ffollowing a suspected assault in
OL,8,FNewcastle as a woman is charged with
OL,9,Fhis murder.
OL,11,FJohn Hardy, 48, was found with serious
OL,12,Finjuries when officers responded to a
OL,13,Freport of a disturbance at an address
OL,14,Fin Sceptre Place, in Elswick, at
OL,15,F6.30pm on Monday (11 November).
OL,17,FNorthumbria Police said his injuries
OL,18,Fwere "consistent with being caused by
OL,19,Fa bladed article" and despite the
OL,20,Fefforts of paramedics, he died a short
OL,21,Ftime later.
