OL,6,FHis next of kin have been informed and
OL,7,Fare being supported by specially-
OL,8,Ftrained officers.
OL,10,FBrenda Heslop, 62, of Sceptre Place,
OL,11,FNewcastle, has been charged with
OL,12,Fmurder and is due to appear before
OL,13,Fmagistrates in the city on Wednesday
OL,14,F(12 November).
OL,16,FOfficers remain in the area to carry
OL,17,Fout enquiries and to offer reassurance
OL,18,Fto the public.
