OL,6,FDetective Inspector Mark Atherton, of
OL,7,Fthe Force's Major Investigation Team,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Our thoughts continue to be
OL,9,Fwith John's family at this extremely
OL,10,Fdifficult time.
OL,12,F"We will offer them all of the support
OL,13,Fwe can as they attempt to process the
OL,14,Fevents of the past couple of days.
OL,16,FDetective Inspector Atherton added: "A
OL,17,Fsuspect has now been charged to appear
OL,18,Fin court and I'd ask that everyone
OL,19,Favoid speculation ` both online and in
OL,20,Fthe community ` and respect the active
OL,21,Flegal proceedings.
